===鈽實驗===

1945年，作為[[曼哈頓計划|曼哈頓計划]]的一部分，[[芝加哥大學|芝加哥大學]]Billings Hospital醫院的三位病人被注射鈽。<ref name="pfiles-146-148">{{Cite book|title=The Plutonium Files: America's Secret Medical Experiments in the Cold War|url=https://archive.org/details/plutoniumfilesam0000wels|author=Eileen Welsome|publisher=Dial Press|location=New York|year=1999|isbn=0-385-31402-7|pages=[https://archive.org/details/plutoniumfilesam0000wels/page/146 146]–148}}</ref>

